content: Muhammad Umair Hassan received a BS in Computer Science from the University of the Punjab, Pakistan in 2017. He is currently pursuing MS in Computer Science from School of Information Science and Engineering, University of Jinan, China. His research interests include deep learning, image processing, computer vision, and machine learning.
